# UXDS E1 Loop Routing

Before implementing or merging UX Design Studio work:

1. Read and follow `AGENTS.md`, including the `E1 Autonomous Loop Exception` when active.
2. Load the canonical story-loop skill at `.agents/skills/uxds-story-loop/SKILL.md`.
3. Invoke the independent read-only verifier contract at `.agents/verifiers/uxds-story-verifier.md` before commit and merge.
4. Respect E1-only autonomy: automatic story chaining and gated self-merge apply only to issues `#2`, `#5`, and `#8` while epic `#1` remains open and not Blocked.
5. Preserve WIP limit 1, signed commits, no direct pushes to `staging` or `main`, and all other hard stops outside the explicit E1 overrides.
6. Keep canonical rules in `.agents/**`; do not duplicate or weaken them here.
